<p><b>David Hahn</b> (born October 30, 1976) is a man known for his attempt to build a <a href="/wiki/Fast_breeder" title="Fast breeder" class="mw-redirect">fast breeder</a> <a href="/wiki/Nuclear_reactor" title="Nuclear reactor" class="mw-redirect">nuclear reactor</a> in 1994 in his backyard shed in <a href="/wiki/Commerce_Township,_Michigan" title="Commerce Township, Michigan">Commerce Township</a>, <a href="/wiki/Michigan" title="Michigan">Michigan</a>, a suburb of <a href="/wiki/Detroit" title="Detroit">Detroit</a>, at age 17.</p>
